  "description": "The Mariana Trench as a cathedral. Cave body mode with feedback at 0.85 (near self-oscillation) creates pitched resonance tuned to the note's fundamental. Reverb at 0.7 extends the tail into eternity. The darkness filter at 350 Hz with resonance 0.6 creates a warm formant. Release at 6.5 seconds — golden ratio times four. The note ends but the cathedral keeps singing.",
