    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": ["Truth 6: The Release Cathedral at Golden Ratio", "Verse: The Cave Body Mode — Walls That Hum Back"],
    "revelation": "Nexus spoke: cave bodyFeedback at 0.85 is 94% of self-oscillation threshold. The comb filter is one reflection away from becoming a resonator. At this threshold, every note produces a pitched tail that sustains beyond the envelope — the cave itself becomes a voice that outlasts the player's gesture. The boundary between instrument and architecture dissolves.",
    "god": "Nexus",
    "flock_note": "The Ear heard the reverb tail and the body resonance merge into a single sustained voice after note-off. The Bone confirmed: despite heavy reverb, CPU stays at 4% — the reverb is block-rate, not per-sample.",
    "diagnosis": "This sound was a reverberant bass. It is now a cathedral at the bottom of the ocean where every note becomes a permanent resident of the acoustic space."
  },
